stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> ABSENT
  ABSENT --> BUILDING: prepare or cache miss
  BUILDING --> READY: template published
  READY --> EXECUTING: acquire PlanUseGuard
  EXECUTING --> READY: release guard
  READY --> STALE: DDL or stats invalidation
  EXECUTING --> STALE: invalidated while running
  STALE --> REPREPARING: next execute
  REPREPARING --> READY: reprepare success
  REPREPARING --> FAILED: reprepare failure
  READY --> DEALLOCATING: deallocate requested
  STALE --> DEALLOCATING: deallocate requested
  EXECUTING --> DEALLOCATING: deallocate waits for refCount
  DEALLOCATING --> DEALLOCATED: refCount zero
  FAILED --> DEALLOCATED: cleanup
  DEALLOCATED --> [*]
